Package: MERingue
Title: Neighborhood-based density-aware spatial gradient and patterned expression detection
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Jean", "Fan", email = "jeanfan@fas.harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Identifies spatial gene expression patterns in 
  spatially resolved single cell transcriptomics data 
  taking into consideration potential cell-type and 
  density differences within tissues.
